name: Meta FPS
public_notice: Project MetaPlayers.gg (FPS) has recently migrated from their old contract to a new one. Visit this post for more information and visit the old token page here.
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is the project about?

MetaPlayersGG is the bridge between eSports and the crypto world. Join our ecosystem and be part of the future of eSports!

What makes your project unique?

Create or join eSport tournaments, complete challenges, play for crypto prizes, find the best teams and the hottest Play 2 Earn games on metaplayers.gg.

What’s next for your project?

An ecosystem with endless possibilities

We’re building a mutually beneficial, tournament-centered network for eSport marketers, content creators, organizers and players alike.

NFTs with purpose

Buy gaming NFTs, passes, in-game items, and pieces of our own utility-focused NFT collection for $MFPS token in the MetaPlayers marketplace.

What can your token be used for?

Reach new audiences in an authentic, noninvasive way through eSports tournament, player, or live stream sponsorship.
